    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The stuff of dreams",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.7,
      "endTime": 10.85
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What is going on when a person experiences rapid eye-movements during sleep?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.86,
      "endTime": 18.36,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "It is fairly clear that the sleeping period must have some function, and because there is so much of it the function would seem to be important.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 18.37,
      "endTime": 28.7,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Much",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Speculations about its nature have been going on for literally thousands of years,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 28.71,
      "endTime": 35.15,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and one odd finding that makes the problem puzzling is that it looks very much as if sleeping is not simply a matter of giving the body a rest.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 35.16,
      "endTime": 45.35,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          },
          {
            "word": "Much",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "非常"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "'Rest', in terms of muscle relaxation and so on, can be achieved by a brief period lying, or even sitting down.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 45.36,
      "endTime": 55.74,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The body's tissues are self-repairing and self-restoring to a degree, and function best when more or less continuously active.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 55.75,
      "endTime": 66.26,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "In fact a basic amount of movement occurs during sleep which is specifically concerned with preventing muscle inactivity.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 66.27,
      "endTime": 75.65,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "If it is not a question of resting the body, then perhaps it is the brain that needs resting?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 75.66,
      "endTime": 83.64,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "This might be a plausible hypothesis were it not for two factors.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 83.65,
      "endTime": 89.36,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "First the electroencephalograph (which is simply a device for recording the electrical activity of the brain by attaching electrodes to the scalp)",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 89.37,
      "endTime": 100.74,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "shows that while there is a change in the pattern of activity during sleep,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 100.75,
      "endTime": 105.79,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "there is no evidence that the total amount of activity is any less.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 105.8,
      "endTime": 111.35,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The second factor is more interesting and more fundamental.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 111.36,
      "endTime": 115.99,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Some years ago an American psychiatrist named William Dement published experiments dealing with the recording of eye-movements during sleep.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 116,
      "endTime": 126.9,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "American",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "美国的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "He showed that the average individual's sleep cycle is punctuated with peculiar bursts of eye-movements, some drifting and slow, others jerky and rapid.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 126.91,
      "endTime": 140.32,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "People woken during these periods of eye-movements generally reported that they had been dreaming.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 140.33,
      "endTime": 146.9,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "When woken at other times they reported no dreams.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 146.91,
      "endTime": 150.84,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "If one group of people were disturbed from their eye-movement sleep for several nights on end,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 150.85,
      "endTime": 156.29,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and another group were disturbed for an equal period of time but when they were not exhibiting eye-movements,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 156.3,
      "endTime": 165.43,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "the first group began to show some personality disorders while the others seemed more or less unaffected.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 165.44,
      "endTime": 174.87
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The implications of all this were that it was not the disturbance of sleep that mattered, but the disturbance of dreaming.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 174.88,
      "endTime": 179.88,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
